title: LF Top Plat 1+ Player for 5s Team
body:
Looking for a top laner for a competitive team, prefer diamond + but will take plat 1.
Need for someone who has a diverse champ pool and is confident in their laning, TP's and communication.
Competitive experience helps but isn't required, just want someone motivated.

Add "The Pinch" ingame for more details

replies.body: Get a bit higher up in the ranks then you can come back to me and ill think about it.
